wdi2-SH.XPD.PVTD.CH.ZS.def: Share of current health expenditures funded from domestic private sources.  Domestic private sources include funds from households, corporations and non-profit organizations. Such expenditures can be either prepaid to voluntary health insurance or paid directly to healthcare providers.
wdi2-SH.XPD.PVTD.CH.ZS.name: Domestic private health expenditure
wdi2-SH.XPD.PVTD.CH.ZS.source: World Health Organization Global Health Expenditure database (http://apps.who.int/nha/database).
